comments: Ivey (DET) places a hand on Banton's (TOR) side as he elevates during the driving shot attempt but the contact is marginal.
Anunoby (TOR) legally contests the jump shot attempt by Ivey (DET), who extends his leg in an attempt to draw contact.
Bey (DET) does not step out of bounds at the start of his drive to the basket.
Barnes (TOR) initiates contact with Bey's (DET) body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Bey (DET) engages with Barnes (TOR) during the rebound and Barnes and Bogdanovic (DET) make incidental foot to foot contact that causes Barnes to trip.
Ivey (DET) is not established in a legal guarding position when body contact occurs with Anunoby (TOR) during his driving shot attempt.
Bogdanovic (DET) does not give a step of distance when establishing himself in Barnes's (TOR) path and illegal contact occurs that affects Barnes's (TOR) ability to defend.
Anunoby (TOR) loses his dribble but does not move from the frontcourt into the backcourt.
Bagley III (DET) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Bagley III (DET) moves into Dowtin Jr.'s (TOR) space during the rebound and dislodges him from his position.
Dowtin Jr. (TOR) lands out of bounds with the ball in his possession.
Dowtin Jr. (TOR) cleanly blocks the driving shot attempt by Ivey (DET) and the body contact is marginal.
Ivey (DET) initiates contact to Banton's (TOR) arm that affects his control of the ball.
Ivey (DET) commits a take foul on Banton (TOR).
Anunoby (TOR) legally contests Bey's (DET) jump shot attempt.
